text-align: left;\">\n                <b>FirstRowSports</b> is a project following the legacy of the well known US site FirstRowSports.com, which was closed by force in 2012 by US authorities. We are a small team that keeps this service alive. Our mirror of the site provides the same that the old one once did  free streaming online videos of sports events of every kind  <b>Football(Soccer), Basketball, Tennis, Moto GP, US Football, Rugby, Hockey, Snooker, Badminton, Table tennis, Volleyball</b> and many others.<br>\nIf you have any problems with the streaming, please check the Troubleshoot link under the player.<br>\nJust FirstRowSports is EU based, and you should check if the laws in your country permit you to visit it. The site is prohibited for US and UK users for this purpose, although it may be accessible due to technical reasons.<br>\nFirstRowSportss mission is to (just) provide you with streams of your favourite sports <i>FREE of charge, no sign ups, no email spam etc.</i> All live streams you watch are not hosted on this site. All ads you see on players, are placed there by the owners of the streams, we only publish embedded links to these.<br>\nWe do not place any ads on the streams, we are only a medium, so that you can find all football, tennis, basketball etc. sport events in one place and watch it without any problems  because as fans we hate it when something stops us from watching our match too.<br>\nWe do not encourage copyright infringements, and we do not carry any responsibility if such a stream gets accidentally published on our site. If you are an owner of copyrighted material featured on our site, please contact us.<br>\nYou can read more on our About us page.
